General.Name: NCAB Group
General.Description: NCAB Group AB (publ) manufactures and sells printed circuit boards (PCBs) worldwide. The company offers multilayer, high-density interconnect, radio frequency, insulated metal base, flexible, rigid-flex, semi-flex, and double-sided PCBs. It serves aerospace and defense, automotive, datacom, industrial, medical, power and energy, railway, safety-critical, and telecom industries. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Sundbyberg, Sweden.
